flowRoot.flowPara: The cross marks where swiping is locked. Swipe left to continue.
Hold left or right side of the screen to lock swiping in that direction.
Oops, now you are locked. Hold again to unlock.
This is sample app of open source library lockable-view-pager.
You can't go further than this slide! It is locked!
You can lock it again if you like - just to see how it works.
Tap the number to lock any slide you like.
